    "title": {
      "rendered": "20 Crowdfunding Services for Nonprofits Worldwide"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22307 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Crowdfunding-Services-for-nonprofits-Twitter.jpg?resize=600%2C315\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"315\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Crowdfunding-Services-for-nonprofits-Twitter.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Crowdfunding-Services-for-nonprofits-Twitter.jpg?resize=300%2C158&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>Nonprofits in North America, Europe, and Australia have a multitude of online fundraising services to choose from mostly thanks to their government&#8217;s efforts to build digital records and databases of legally verified nonprofits. In most parts of the world, however, government&#8217;s digital capabilities remain a work in progress and as a result, the ability to accept online donations is challenging for most nonprofits in Africa, parts of Asia, Eastern Europe, the Middle East, and Latin America.</p>\n<p>To fill in the gap, social good\u00a0entrepreneurs worldwide have built upon the momentum of <a href=\"https://www.entrepreneur.com/article/228125\"><strong>crowdfunding</strong></a> and extended crowdfunding services to nonprofits, NGOs, and charities in regions where online fundraising has been challenging up to this point in the Internet&#8217;s short history. The services themselves have taken on the responsibility of vetting the nonprofits and for that alone, deserve muchos kudos.</p>\n<p>That said, this year&#8217;s <a href=\"https://givingreport.ngo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Global Trends in Giving Survey</strong></a> includes questions about crowdfunding. If you are a donor, please volunteer 4-7 minutes of your time and take the survey.</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. BackaBuddy (South Africa)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.backabuddy.co.za\">backabuddy.co.za</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.backabuddy.co.za\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22254\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/BackaBuddy2-2.jpg?resize=600%2C369\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"369\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/BackaBuddy2-2.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/BackaBuddy2-2.jpg?resize=300%2C185&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. Donate-ng (Nigeria)<br />\n<a href=\"https://donate-ng.com\">donate-ng.com</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://donate-ng.com\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22267\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/donate-nigeria-2.jpg?resize=600%2C355\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"355\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/donate-nigeria-2.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/donate-nigeria-2.jpg?resize=300%2C178&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. M-Changa (Kenya)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.changa.co.ke\">changa.co.ke</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://changa.co.ke\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22247\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/m-changa.jpg?resize=600%2C346\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"346\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/m-changa.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/m-changa.jpg?resize=300%2C173&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Asia</h1>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. GIVE.asia (Multiple Countries)<br />\n<a href=\"https://give.asia\">give.asia</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://give.asia\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22261\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/giveasia.jpg?resize=600%2C361\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"361\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/giveasia.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/giveasia.jpg?resize=300%2C181&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">5. Giving.sg (Singapore)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.giving.sg\">giving.sg</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.giving.sg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22260\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/giving.sg_.jpg?resize=600%2C350\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/giving.sg_.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/giving.sg_.jpg?resize=300%2C175&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">6. Ketto (India)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ketto.org\">ketto.org</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.ketto.org\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22256\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Ketto.jpg?resize=600%2C373\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"373\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Ketto.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Ketto.jpg?resize=300%2C187&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Australia &amp; Oceania</h1>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">7. everydayhero (Australia)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.everydayhero.com/au/\">everydayhero.com/au</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.everydayhero.com/au/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22268\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/everydayhero.jpg?resize=600%2C352\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"352\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/everydayhero.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/everydayhero.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">8. GiveaLittle (New Zealand)<br />\n<a href=\"https://givealittle.co.nz\">givealittle.co.nz</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://givealittle.co.nz\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22269\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Give-A-Little.jpg?resize=600%2C376\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"376\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Give-A-Little.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Give-A-Little.jpg?resize=300%2C188&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Europe</h1>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">9. Goteo (Spain)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.goteo.org\">goteo.org</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.goteo.org\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22271\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Goteo.jpg?resize=600%2C324\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"324\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Goteo.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Goteo.jpg?resize=300%2C162&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">10. HelloAsso (France)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.helloasso.com\">helloasso.com</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.helloasso.com\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22273\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/HelloAsso.jpg?resize=600%2C337\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/HelloAsso.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/HelloAsso.jpg?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">11. iDonate (Ireland)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.idonate.ie\">idonate.ie</a></h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.idonate.ie\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22275\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/iDonate.jpg?resize=600%2C357\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"357\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/iDonate.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/iDonate.jpg?resize=300%2C179&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><br />\n12. JustGiving (United Kingdom)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.justgiving.com\">justgiving.com</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.justgiving.com\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22279\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/JustGiving2.jpg?resize=600%2C342\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"342\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/JustGiving2.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/JustGiving2.jpg?resize=300%2C171&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<p>The<strong>\u00a0<a href=\"https://givingreport.ngo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-cke-saved-href=\"https://givingreport.ngo\">2018 Global Trends in Giving Survey</a></strong>\u00a0is an annual research project that seeks to gain a better understanding of how donors worldwide prefer to give and engage with their favorite causes and charitable organizations. If you have donated to a nonprofit, NGO, or charity within the last 12 months, then please take the survey! Available in five languages \u2013\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https://givingreport.ngo/ar/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-cke-saved-href=\"https://givingreport.ngo/ar/\">\u0627\u0644\u0639\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651\u0629</a></strong>,\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https://givingreport.ngo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-cke-saved-href=\"https://givingreport.ngo\">English</a></strong>,\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https://givingreport.ngo/fr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-cke-saved-href=\"https://givingreport.ngo/fr/\">fran\u00e7ais</a>, <a href=\"https://givingreport.ngo/pt-br/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-cke-saved-href=\"https://givingreport.ngo/pt-br/\">portugu\u00eas</a></strong>, and\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https://givingreport.ngo/es/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-cke-saved-href=\"https://givingreport.ngo/es/\">espa\u00f1ol</a></strong>\u00a0\u2013\u00a0the survey will be live through June 30 and the results will be released on September 17 in the second edition of the Global Trends in Giving Report.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://givingreport.ngo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22282\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/For-MailChimp.jpg?resize=600%2C315\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"315\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/For-MailChimp.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/For-MailChimp.jpg?resize=300%2C158&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">North America</h1>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">13. CanadaHelps<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.canadahelps.org/en/fundraise/\">canadahelps.org</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.canadahelps.org/en/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22287\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/CanadaHelps2.jpg?resize=600%2C353\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"353\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/CanadaHelps2.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/CanadaHelps2.jpg?resize=300%2C177&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">14. Crowdrise (Canada and the United States)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.crowdrise.com/online-fundraising\">crowdrise.com</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.crowdrise.com/online-fundraising\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22293\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Crowdrise.jpg?resize=600%2C330\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"330\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Crowdrise.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Crowdrise.jpg?resize=300%2C165&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">15. Donadora (Mexico)<br />\n<a href=\"https://donadora.mx\">donadora.mx</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://donadora.mx\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22292\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Donadora-3.jpg?resize=600%2C359\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"359\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Donadora-3.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Donadora-3.jpg?resize=300%2C180&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">16. Generosity (United States)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.generosity.com\">generosity.com</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.generosity.com\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22294\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Generosity.jpg?resize=600%2C370\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"370\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Generosity.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Generosity.jpg?resize=300%2C185&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">South America</h1>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">17. Doare (Brazil)<br />\n<a href=\"https://doare.org/br/\">doare.org</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://doare.org/br/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22295\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Doare.jpg?resize=600%2C333\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Doare.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Doare.jpg?resize=300%2C167&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">18. Ideame (Multiple Countries)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.idea.me\">idea.me</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.idea.me\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22296\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Idea.me_.jpg?resize=600%2C350\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Idea.me_.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Idea.me_.jpg?resize=300%2C175&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">19. Yo Dono (Chile)<br />\n<a href=\"https://yodono.cl\">yodono.cl</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://yodono.cl\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22298\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Yo-Dono.jpg?resize=600%2C385\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"385\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Yo-Dono.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Yo-Dono.jpg?resize=300%2C193&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Global</h1>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">GlobalGiving<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org\">globalgiving.org</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22299\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/global-giving.jpg?resize=600%2C291\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"291\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/global-giving.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/global-giving.jpg?resize=300%2C146&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<p>Now in its third year, the\u00a0<strong><a href=\"http://techreport.ngo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-cke-saved-href=\"http://techreport.ngo\">2018 Global NGO Technology Report</a></strong>\u00a0is based upon the survey results of 5,352 NGOs from 164 countries and available in\u00a0<strong><a href=\"http://techreport.ngo/ar/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-cke-saved-href=\"http://techreport.ngo/ar/\">\u0627\u0644\u0639\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651\u0629</a></strong>,\u00a0<strong><a href=\"http://techreport.ngo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-cke-saved-href=\"http://techreport.ngo\">English</a></strong>,\u00a0<strong><a href=\"http://techreport.ngo/fr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-cke-saved-href=\"http://techreport.ngo/fr/\">fran\u00e7ais</a></strong>, <strong><a href=\"http://techreport.ngo/pt-br/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-cke-saved-href=\"http://techreport.ngo/pt-br/\">portugu\u00eas</a></strong>, and\u00a0<strong><a href=\"http://techreport.ngo/es/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-cke-saved-href=\"http://techreport.ngo/es/\">espa\u00f1ol</a></strong>.\u00a0The report is groundbreaking in that it is the only annual research project dedicated to studying how NGOs worldwide use web and email communications, online fundraising tools, social media, mobile technology, and data management and security software.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://techreport.ngo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22066\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/blog.jpg?resize=600%2C315\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"315\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/blog.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/blog.jpg?resize=300%2C158&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n",
      "protected": false
    },
    "excerpt": {
      "rendered": "<p>Nonprofits in North America, Europe, and Australia have a multitude of online fundraising services to choose from mostly thanks to their government&#8217;s efforts to build digital records and databases of legally verified nonprofits. In most parts of the world, however, government&#8217;s digital capabilities remain a work in progress and as a result, the ability to accept online donations is challenging for most nonprofits in Africa, parts of Asia, Eastern Europe, the Middle East, and Latin America. To fill in the gap, social good\u00a0entrepreneurs worldwide have built upon the momentum of crowdfunding and extended crowdfunding services to nonprofits, NGOs, and charities </p>\n",
      "protected": false
    },
